6 cups rice krispy treats
1 cup peanut butter
1 cup sugar
1 cup karo (corn syrup)

Mix sugar and karo and heat until just boiling.
Mix in peanut butter and re-heat until just boiling.
Take off heat and stir in rice krispys.
Spread into pan, and let cool.

(Don't over-cook. Just heat until you see the first bubbles.)
